CONTENT:
Dear Mohammad,


It is with great pleasure Inkspell announces the 6th annual edition of India Content Leadership Awards 2023

Our research shows that TEDx has done some remarkable content production/promotion work, and it could be a potential contender for the ICL 6.0.


ICL Awards by Inkspell Media has been one of the most prestigious recognition for India's content industry over the last few years, and it honors excellence in the following broad categories:


  1. Content as a Product
  2. Content as a Service
  3. Content as an Enabler
  4. Overall Content Excellence

Entries are closing soon. Send your nominations now at www.IndiaContentLeadership.com

Join the league of Industry Icons! Submit entries now!

Please feel free to reach out to me to discuss this further.


Regards,

Geetika Kaushal

CONVERSATION TITLE: Unleash revolutionary technology and workflows with Z by H
CONTENT:
Hi Mohammad,


Architects, manufacturers, data science and creative professionals, and educators all face the same barrier to brilliance in today’s digital era: high-performance computing power on demand. To unleash new competitive differentiators, they need to leverage revolutionary technologies like 3D printing, photogrammetry, and AI-based analytics to optimize workflows and enhance productivity.


HP Z Desktop Workstations overcome this obstacle with powerful NVIDIA graphics, multi-core processors, large memory, and storage configurations – built to power through today’s heaviest workloads.


In addition, HP Anyware lets the performance of Z Desktop Workstations accessible remotely, seamlessly, and securely. With this powerful on-demand remote compute experience, 3D or VR developers, data analysts, and other power users can work and collaborate on the most computing-intensive projects anywhere.


Z Desktop Workstations also come preloaded with Windows Subsystem for Linux (WSL 2), which integrates the benefits of Windows and Linux in a single package. Without the need to dual-boot or maintain separate systems, data science and technical practitioners can accelerate workflows in an Ubuntu environment with all the manageability and security of established Windows infrastructure.


Find out more about how Z Desktop Workstations deliver limitless performance,

momentum, and innovation to drive borderless business ambitions.

To unleash new competitive differentiators, they need to leverage revolutionary technologies like 3D printing, photogrammetry, and AI-based analytics to optimize workflows and enhance productivity.


HP Z Desktop Workstations overcome this obstacle with powerful NVIDIA graphics, multi-core processors, large memory, and storage configurations – built to power through today’s heaviest workloads.

Z Desktop Workstations also come preloaded with Windows Subsystem for Linux (WSL 2), which integrates the benefits of Windows and Linux in a single package. Without the need to dual-boot or maintain separate systems, data science and technical practitioners can accelerate workflows in an Ubuntu environment with all the manageability and security of established Windows infrastructure.
